(73380, 132418, 0, 1, 'Circle 圈 (Original Mix)', 'Eds - Circle 圈 (Original Mix)\n\n新年快樂 各位！我是Eds，Circle 圈 (Original Mix) 是我2014年的第一發，一樣延續了對Progressive House的熱愛，一樣是挑了銷魂女聲的Vocal來詮釋，然後用了很多空間效果來製作，希望大家會喜歡，也在新的一年送上新的歌曲給各位來當祝福！\n\nHappy new year guys! Edison here. This song, Circle (Original Mix) is my first song as of 2014, and it''s produced mainly to reflect my love towards Progressive House music. Some of the elements applied in this new piece are the fetching vocal, and spacing effects. I very much do hope you guys like it, and I hope this brings you a different 2014!  \n\n歌詞 lyrics \nOrdinary people chasing stars\nStop and wonder who they really are\nBut the circles keep on closing around them\nFascinating fires draw them in\nPromises of love thrown to the wind\nBut the circles never open for them\nTake a look x\n\nLike in circles no beginning\nLove is endless never ending\n\nOrdinary people chasing stars\nStop and wonder who they really are\nBut the circles keep on closing around them\nFascinating fires draw them in\nPromises of love thrown to the wind\nBut the circles never open for them\nTake a look x\n\nFacebook \nhttp://www.facebook.com/DJEdsTaiwan\n\nFanpage \nhttp://www.facebook.com/DJEds\n\nYoutube \nhttp://www.youtube.com/EdsTaiwan\n\nSoundcloud \nhttp://soundcloud.com/djeds\n\nMixCloud \nhttp://www.mixcloud.com/DJEds\n\n\n個人聯絡信箱：\n\ndj.eds@hotmail.com', '2014-02-02 00:00:00', 2014, 30, 1, 3, 'Ordinary people chasing stars\nStop and wonder who they really are\nBut the circles keep on closing around them\nFascinating fires draw them in\nPromises of love thrown to the wind\nBut the circles never open for them\nTake a look x\n\nLike in circles no beginning\nLove is endless never ending\n\nOrdinary people chasing stars\nStop and wonder who they really are\nBut the circles keep on closing around them\nFascinating fires draw them in\nPromises of love thrown to the wind\nBut the circles never open for them\nTake a look x', '', 353, '', 'Eds', '', 'Eds', 'Eds Music