(73384, 132418, 0, 1, 'Till Tonight (Eds Remix)', 'Laidback Luke Feat Jonathan Mendelson - Till Tonight (Eds Remix)\n我的朋友你們好！我是Eds，Till Tonight (Eds Remix) 是我混一個我非常喜歡的DJ製作人叫做Laidback Luke，雖然這首是老歌，但還是要老歌新玩一下，裡面我只選用Jonathan Mendelson的聲音而已，也是第一次做這樣的Remix，希望大家會喜歡，這首會讓大家免費下載！2014年還需要更多你們的支持，我會繼續成長的！\n\nLaidback Luke Feat Jonathan Mendelson - Till Tonight (Eds Remix) \nHow are you my friends! I am Eds, Till Tonight (Eds Remix) I mix one of my very favorite DJ producer called Laidback Luke, though the song is a old song,  but still want to play with it, I only used Jonathan Mendelson''s voice only, and its the first time i did a Remix like this, hope you will like it and it will be a free download! 2014 also requires more of your support, I will continue to grow!\n\nFacebook \nhttp://www.facebook.com/DJEdsTaiwan\n\nFanpage \nhttp://www.facebook.com/DJEds\n\nYoutube \nhttp://www.youtube.com/EdsTaiwan\n\nSoundcloud \nhttp://soundcloud.com/djeds\n\nMixCloud \nhttp://www.mixcloud.com/DJEds\n\n個人聯絡信箱：\n\ndj.eds@hotmail.com', '2014-03-18 00:00:00', 2014, 30, 1, 3, 'I''ve been saving up all my strength for this very day\nAnd now that I''m standing at the gate\n\nOpen up your arms\nAnd spread them wide\nNothing''s gonna hold me back this time\nI''ve been waiting for you all my life\nCounting down the minutes till tonight\n\nOpen up you heart\nAnd let me in\nLet the love finally begin\nCause I''ve been waiting for you all my life\nCounting down every minute until tonight', '', 281, '', 'Eds', '', 'Eds', 'Eds Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-03-19 16:39:28', '2015-03-12 14:05:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
